data.clean_description: Strain Highlights. Pineapple. Express combines the potent and flavorful forces of parent strains Trainwreck and Hawaiian. This hard - hitting sativa provides a long - lasting energetic buzz perfect for productive afternoons and creative escapes. ps good for resell.
